; NAME:
;       CAPFIRSTLETTER
;
; PURPOSE:
;
;       Given a string, separates the parts by white space, commas,
;       semi-colons, or colons. Each part has the first letter capitalized.
;       The returned string has the capitalized parts separated by a space.
